title: Twilight's Last Gleaming (1977)
description:
This is based on lunarredalchemist's upload of the film. 

Now in compact .avi form and in widescreen edition (not sure if 100 % correct aspect ratio, but looks better than overdrawn source!). As a negative side effect, split screens are reduced in size (due to double widescreen beams), but general viewing experience is better, as stuttering is also removed.



File size: 1,46 Gb

Resolution: 624 x 352

Frame rate: 29,97

Duration: 2 h 24 min


You're welcome. And, please, remember to seed!
